<li id="cite_note-Bateson_1972-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Bateson_1972_15-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFBateson.2C_Gregory1972">Bateson, Gregory (1972). <i>Steps to an Ecology of Mind: Collected Essays in Anthropology, Psychiatry, Evolution, and Epistemology</i>. University Of Chicago Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0226039056" class="internal">ISBN 0-226-03905-6</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Steps+to+an+Ecology+of+Mind%3A+Collected+Essays+in+Anthropology%2C+Psychiatry%2C+Evolution%2C+and+Epistemology&amp;rft.aulast=Bateson%2C+Gregory&amp;rft.au=Bateson%2C+Gregory&amp;rft.date=1972&amp;rft.pub=University+Of+Chicago+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-226-03905-6&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Gregory_Bateson"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
